collectors.titleDetails: (3 total Queries, 3 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `b`.*, `us`.`fullname`, `total_item`, `unknown_upc` FROM `assign_report_box` as `b` LEFT JOIN (SELECT box_name, COUNT(assign_report_details.sku) as total_item FROM assign_report_details WHERE item_description <> "ITEM NOT FOUND" GROUP BY box_name) as t ON `t`.`box_name` = `b`.`box_name` LEFT JOIN (SELECT box_name, COUNT(assign_report_details.sku) as unknown_upc FROM assign_report_details WHERE item_description = "ITEM NOT FOUND" GROUP BY box_name) as u ON `u`.`box_name` = `b`.`box_name` JOIN `users` as `us` ON `b`.`user_id` = `us`.`id` WHERE `date_assigned` BETWEEN "2023-10-25 00:00:00" AND "2023-10-26 00:00:00" GROUP BY `b`.`id` ORDER BY `b`.`date_assigned` DESC

SELECT SUM(assign_report_details.qty) as qty, SUM(assign_report_details.original) as original, SUM(assign_report_details.cost) as cost FROM `assign_report_box` JOIN `assign_report_details` ON `assign_report_details`.`box_name` = `assign_report_box`.`box_name` WHERE `date_assigned` BETWEEN "2023-10-25 00:00:00" AND "2023-10-26 00:00:00"
